== 發行 ==
《歡樂好聲音》在[[2016年多倫多國際影展|2016年多倫多國際影展]]上，以特別放映的身分首映<ref name=DeadlineLiveToronto>{{cite web|last1=Hammond|first1=Pete|title=Universal & Illumination To Launch ‘Sing’ With Live Jennifer Hudson And Tori Kelly Performances At Toronto|url=http://deadline.com/2016/08/universal-sing-jennifer-hudson-tori-kelly-toronto-film-festival-1201807483/|publisher=Deadline|accessdate=2016-09-11|date=2016-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160913084228/http://deadline.com/2016/08/universal-sing-jennifer-hudson-tori-kelly-toronto-film-festival-1201807483/|archive-date=2016-09-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[環球影業|環球影業]]定於2016年12月21日於美國發行<ref>{{cite news|last1=McClintock|first1=Pamela|title=Universal Dates 'Despicable Me 3,' New 'Grinch Who Stole Christmas'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/universal-dates-despicable-me-3-671303|accessdate=2015-08-03|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2014-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140118002827/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/universal-dates-despicable-me-3-671303|archive-date=2014-01-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
電影的評價以正面居多。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於187條評論，新鮮度72%，平均評分6.50／10<ref name="RT">{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sing_2016 |title=Sing (2016) |publisher=[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]] |accessdate=2016-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223225845/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sing_2016 |archive-date=2016-12-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分59<ref name="Meta">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/sing |title=Sing reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2016-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222041142/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/sing |archive-date=2016-12-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[影院评分|影院评分]]調查，觀眾的評價在A+至F間落於「A」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=影院评分|work=cinemascore.com|access-date=2019-07-23 |archive-url=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20170916153548/https://m.cinemascore.com/ |archive-date=2017-09-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
電影將在北美與《[[星際過客|星際過客]]》及《[[刺客教條_(電影)|刺客教條]]》共同競爭，預計能在上映五天內收穫7000萬美元<ref name="preview">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/12/rogue-one-star-wars-passengers-jennifer-lawrence-sing-collateral-beauty-will-smith-christmas-box-office-1201869720/ |title=Will ‘Rogue One’ Vanquish The Christmas B.O. Competition? |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |access-date=2016-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161216145243/http://deadline.com/2016/12/rogue-one-star-wars-passengers-jennifer-lawrence-sing-collateral-beauty-will-smith-christmas-box-office-1201869720/ |archive-date=2016-12-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。北美週二票房為170萬美元<ref name="Thursday">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-sing-beats-assassins-creed-passengers-tuesday-previews-958235 |title='Sing's' Box-Office Debut Tops 'Assassin's Creed,' 'Passengers' in Tuesday Night Previews |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=2016-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222041214/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-sing-beats-assassins-creed-passengers-tuesday-previews-958235 |archive-date=2016-12-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。美國首週六天票房收入7670萬美元，位居當週票房第二。

中国大陆方面，最終累计2.15亿人民币<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cbooo.cn/m/658818 |title=欢乐好声音（2017） |access-date=2017-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313045047/http://www.cbooo.cn/m/658818 |archive-date=2017-03-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

台灣方面，首週三天票房為新台幣1950萬元<ref>{{cite news |title=大賣近2千萬！【歡樂好聲音】勇奪全台首周票房冠軍 |url=http://www.worldscreen.com.tw/goods.php?goods_id=13033 |work=世界電影雜誌 |date=2016-12-14 |access-date=2018-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180804140649/http://www.worldscreen.com.tw/goods.php?goods_id=13033 |archive-date=2018-08-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；最終全台票房為新台幣6490萬元<ref name="tfi0505">{{cite web |title=全國電影票房截至2017年四月前資訊 |url=https://www.tfi.org.tw/Content/TFI/PublicInfo/全國電影票房截至2017年四月前資訊_0505v3.pdf |website=[[國家電影中心|國家電影中心]] |date=2017-05-05 |access-date=2019-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612143732/https://www.tfi.org.tw/Content/TFI/PublicInfo/%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E7%A5%A8%E6%88%BF%E6%88%AA%E8%87%B32017%E5%B9%B4%E5%9B%9B%E6%9C%88%E5%89%8D%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A_0505v3.pdf |archive-date=2018-06-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。


